{"name":"Vos Flyggdottir","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Aire","alignment":"CG","hitDice":"7","armorName":"hide armor","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"11 (16 with _barkskin_)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"27 (5d8 + 5)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"10","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"17","chaPoints":"13","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The druid can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The druid regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the druid can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the druid can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The druid can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the druid's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the druid's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the druid dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"Vos is a 3rd-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 13, +5 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following cleric spells prepared:\n\n\n> * Cantrips (at will): _thaumaturgy, produce flame, shillelagh_\n> * 1st level (4 slots): _cure wounds, speak with animals, thunderwave_\n> * 2nd level (3 slots): _animal messenger, calm emotions, spike growth_\n> * 3rd level (1 slots): _water walk_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Quarterstaff","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit (+4 to hit with shillelagh), reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 3 (1d6) bludgeoning damage, or 6 (1d8 + 2) bludgeoning damage with shillelagh or if wielded with two hands."},{"name":"Turn Undead","desc":"Each undead that can see or hear you within 30  must make a DC 13 Wisdom saving throw. If the creature fails its saving throw, it is turned for 1 minute or until it takes any damage.\n\nA turned creature must spend its turns trying to move as far away from Vos as it can, and it can't willingly move to a space within 30 feet of Vos. It also can't take reactions. For its action, it can use only the Dash action or try to escape from an effect that prevents it from moving. If there's nowhere to move, the creature can use the Dodge action."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"medicine","stat":"wis"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}